body:
@adamjstewart 

As a proposal, I was wondering if `build_type` method in the CMakePackage could be set by default as:

```
def build_type(self):
        spec = self.spec
        if '+debug' in spec:
            return 'Debug'
        else:
            return 'Release'
```

I think that most of CMakePackage packages define the build type in that way, but I don't know if there is any other reason to leave it to the user.
